  },
  {
    title: 'Critical MOU Elements',
    id: 'elements',
    items: [
      {
        heading: 'Recitals & Background',
        body: 'The "whereas" clauses establishing context and party relationships. While often considered non-binding, these sections inform interpretation of substantive terms.'
      },
      {
        heading: 'Scope of Understanding',
        body: 'What the parties agree to explore or undertake. Translation must distinguish between firm commitments and areas for future negotiation.'
      },
      {
